quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,18,jo shakhs duniya ( ki aasoudgi ) ka khawahish mand ho to hum is mein se jisay chahtay hain aur jitna chahtay hain jald day dete hain. phir is ke liye jahannum ko ( thikana ) muqarrar kar rakha hai. jis mein woh nafreen sun kar aur ( dargaah khuda se ) raandah ho kar daakhil hoga
  17,19,aur jo shakhs akhirat ka khawastgah howa aur is mein itni koshish kere jitni usay Laiq hai aur woh momin bhi ho to aisay hi logon ki koshish thikaane lagti hai
  17,20,hum unn ko aur un ko sab ko tumahray perwar-digaar ki bakhshish se madad dete hain. aur tumahray perwar-digaar ki bakhshish ( kisi se ) ruki hui nahi
  17,21,dekho hum ne kis terhan baaz ko baaz par fazeelat bakhsh hai. aur akhirat darjon mein ( duniya se ) bohat bartar aur bartari mein kahin barh kar hai
  17,22,aur khuda ke sath koi aur mabood nah banana ke mlammatain sun kar aur baykas ho kar baithy reh jao ge
  17,23,aur tumahray perwar-digaar ne irshad farmaya hai ke is ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karo aur maa baap ke sath bhalai karte raho. agar un mein se aik ya dono tumahray samnay burhapay ko poanch jayen to unn ko uff taq nah kehna aur nah inhen jhidakna aur unn se baat adab ke sath karna
  17,24,aur ijzo niaz se un ke agay jhuke raho aur un ke haq mein dua karo ke ae perwar-digaar jaissa unhon ne mujhe bachpan mein ( shafqat se ) parwarishkiya hai to bhi unn ( ke haal ) par rehmat farma
  17,25,jo kuch tumahray dilon mein hai tumhara perwar-digaar is se bakhoobi waaqif hai. agar tum naik hogay to woh rujoo laane walon ko bakhash dainay wala hai
  17,26,aur rishta daaron aur mohtajon aur musafiron ko un ka haq ada karo. aur fuzool kharchi se maal nah urrao
  17,27,ke fuzool kharchi karne walay to shetan ke bhai hain. aur shetan apne perwar-digaar ( ki nematon ) ka kufar un karne wala ( yani nashukara ) hai
